      <title>象牙海岸在较小的收获中提高了新作物的可可价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/ivory-coast-raises-cocoa-price-for-new-crop-amid-smaller-harvest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[顶级可可种植者象牙海岸提高了对豆子的价格付出的价格，因为他们期望较小的收获，从而略微缩小了与全球市场的差距。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/ivory-coast-raises-cocoa-price-for-new-crop-amid-smaller-harvest</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 11:56:45 GMT</pubDate>
