      <title>泰晤士水名cfo作为公用事业赛事修理财务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/thames-water-appoints-steve-buck-as-cfo-effective-april-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士河沃特（Thames Water）任命史蒂夫·巴克（Steve Buck）为首席财务官，负责对一家企业进行大修，并由大量的债务压制。]]></description>
