      <title>印度新的印度储备银行代表增加了案件，以削减更高的税率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/india-names-former-world-bank-economist-gupta-as-rbi-deputy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[分析师说，印度的任命Poonam Gupta是前世界银行经济学家Poonam Gupta，他曾提倡较低的利率，从而提高了亚洲第三大经济体货币政策缓解货币政策的案件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/india-names-former-world-bank-economist-gupta-as-rbi-deputy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 09:32:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布鲁克菲尔德说，要复兴有关潜在的Grifols报价的谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/brookfield-is-said-to-revive-talks-on-potential-grifols-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士称，布鲁克菲尔德资产管理有限公司（Brookfield Asset Management Ltd.）恢复了与Grifols SA的主要股东进行谈判，该股东去年尝试失败了，这是西班牙血统公司的潜在报价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/brookfield-is-said-to-revive-talks-on-potential-grifols-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 08:22:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
